casebody.data:
Wednesday, June 8, 1988

MERIT DOCKET

88-499. State, ex rel. Pike Cty. Republican Executive Commt., v. Brown.

In Mandamus. On answer of respondent. Answer treated as motion to dismiss. Motion to dismiss sustained. Cause dismissed.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur. Holmes and Douglas, JJ., dissent.
